Egyptian center under the Ministry of Communications and Information Technology. Established in 2001, the SECC is part of the Egyptian government's strategy to enhance the IT and software industry in Egypt. The center aims to improve the efficiency and competitiveness of Egyptian companies operating in the software and IT sectors.
